125
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,600
Chicken?

126
00:08:43,800 --> 00:08:44,720
Beef?

127
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:46,560
-What do you want?
-Fanxing.

128
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:48,680
