204
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:07,280
<i>No time to explain.</i>

205
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,800
<i>Canyang is going up.</i>

206
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:11,320
<i>Hide if you don't want to get caught.</i>

207
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:13,600
