is so full of collagen.

332
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:36,320
However, he's not a luxurious pet
who depends on branded goods.

333
00:21:37,080 --> 00:21:38,040
We are

334
00:21:38,320 --> 00:21:40,840
having a relationship based on

335
