mutual respect and freedom.

336
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:46,120
Then,

337
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:49,240
what about his--

338
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:51,240
Cut it off!

339
00:21:51,760 --> 00:21:52,800
