He hasn't brought me the detergent yet.

350
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:59,920
<i>Baby, you were not home,
so I took the liberty of coming in.</i>

351
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:01,560
<i>I made your favorite dishes.</i>

352
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:03,440
<i>There's braised stew in the fridge.</i>

353
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:04,760
