496
00:30:53,560 --> 00:30:54,560
Let me think.

497
00:30:55,840 --> 00:30:57,400
Does Canyang know too?

498
00:30:58,760 --> 00:30:59,680
No.

499
00:30:59,920 --> 00:31:01,360
