537
00:33:51,240 --> 00:33:52,760
No. Two hours maximum.

538
00:34:03,080 --> 00:34:04,080
Then,

539
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:06,840
do you want to eat the noodles first

540
00:34:07,560 --> 00:34:08,960
or...

541
00:34:10,240 --> 00:34:11,280
